---
title: Spiced Tofu Loaded Naan with tossed baby gem salad
description: A soft and warm naan is topped with a spicy and slightly sweet curry made up of tender bell peppers and crispy tofu. The dish is rounded out with a vibrant baby gem and radish salad.
